(338, 'GTag', 'Widget', '1''st Paragraph', NULL, '<p>Conference Details The Department of Energy intends to host a non-mandatory bidders'' conference in respect of the Large REIPP Programme. Accordingly, the Department hereby invites parties with an interest to submit proposals adopting any of onshore wind, solar thermal, solar photovoltaic, biomass, biogas, landfill gas or small hydro technologies for any of the third, fourth or fifth bid submission phases under the Large REIPP Programme to attend the bidders'' conference.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Conference Objectives The conference is intended to address the requirements of the RFP in respect of Bid Windows 3, 4 and 5 as well as providing bidders with feedback from the Department in relation to areas of concern arising from Bid Windows 1 & 2. It is important to highlight that of the 3 625 MW allocated to the Large REIPP programme, 2 459,4 MW has been allocated in Bid Windows 1 and 2 with a further 1 165,6 MW available for Bid Windows 3, 4 and 5.</p>\r\n\r\n', 's:0:"";', '', '', '*', '2013-02-17', '2012-12-12', 0, 350),
